HEADWORD: Tenotomy
<hw>Te*not"o*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>te`nwn</grk> a tendon + <grk>te`mnein</grk> to cut.]</ety>
